object.script:
local out_per_launch = property.getNumber("Outputs per launch (for example, 1 for a missile, 4 for a missile pod)") local current_launch_number = 0
local limit_behaviour = property.getBool("Limit Reached Behaviour")
local hold = property.getBool("Press or Hold Output")
function onTick() local total_launches = input.getNumber(1) local launch = input.getBool(1) if launch and total_launches * out_per_launch > current_launch_number then if not hold then output.setBool(math.ceil(current_launch_number/out_per_launch), false) end output.setNumber(1, 0) current_launch_number = current_launch_number + 1 output.setBool(math.ceil(current_launch_number/out_per_launch), true) else if limit_behvaiour then current_launch_number = 0 else output.setNumber(1, 1) end end end

=2 and a(b)<=l then o(0,0,"VALID yaw thrsh: "..(au):format(l)..at..(au):format(f<=1 and a(q*k-b)or f>=2 and a(b)))else o(0,0,"INVALID yaw thrsh: "..(au):format(l)..at..(au):format(f<=1 and a(q*k-b)or f>=2 and a(b)))end else o(0,0,"horizontal_rot doesnt exist")end if p then if g<=1 and a(p*i-c)<=m or g>=2 and a(c)<=m then o(0,20,"VALID pitch thrsh: "..(au):format(m)..as..(au):format(g<=1 and a(p*i-c)or g>=2 and a(c)))else o(0,20,"INVALID pitch thrsh: "..(au):format(m)..as..(au):format(g<=1 and a(p*i-c)or g>=2 and a(c)))end else o(0,20,"vertical_rot doesnt exist")end end end function n.W(j,min,max)return maxj and min or j end function d(j)return j~=j and 0 or j end function ab(j,min,max)return(j-min)/(max-min)%1*(max-min)+min end

object.script:
-- Simple EPN, by Lassi#9944
lastRateX=0 lastRateY=0 lastAccX=0 lastAccY=0
navRate=property.getNumber("Rate nav") navAcc=property.getNumber("Acc nav") navJerk=property.getNumber("Jerk nav")
smoothclosingv=0
function onTick() rateX=input.getNumber(1) rateY=input.getNumber(2) closingv=-input.getNumber(3) distance=input.getNumber(4) guide=input.getBool(1) --smoothclosingv=smoothclosingv+(closingv-smoothclosingv)/2 smoothclosingv=closingv Tgo=math.min(distance/math.max(closingv*60,1),10)
accX=rateX-lastRateX accY=rateY-lastRateY jerkX=accX-lastAccX jerkY=accY-lastAccY
if accX==rateX then accX=0 end if accY==rateY then accY=0 end if jerkX==jerkX then jerkX=0 end if jerkY==jerkY then jerkY=0 end
if guide == true then output.setNumber(1,(rateX*navRate*math.abs(smoothclosingv) + accX*navAcc*Tgo^2 + jerkX*navJerk*Tgo)*property.getNumber("Yaw multiplier")) output.setNumber(2,(rateY*navRate*math.abs(smoothclosingv) + accY*navAcc*Tgo^2 + jerkY*navJerk*Tgo)*property.getNumber("Pitch multiplier")) end
output.setNumber(3,rateX) output.setNumber(4,rateY) output.setNumber(5,closingv) output.setNumber(6,smoothclosingv)
lastRateX=rateX lastRateY=rateY lastAccX=accX lastAccY=accY end

tab={} function onTick() value=input.getNumber(1) if value ~= 0 and math.abs(value) < 100 then table.insert(tab,value) end total=0 for i,v in ipairs(tab) do total=total+v end total=total/#tab if #tab>6 then table.remove(tab,1) end
if #tab==0 then total=0 end
output.setNumber(1, total) output.setNumber(2, input.getNumber(2)) end
